{"tid":409602,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"freelance project 個客突然唔做，尾數點算？","createTime":"2017-09-22T08:00:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T04:32:05.000Z","uid":53194,"like":6,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eb30838dd12e122b72a38d268d5a969419d8768d","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:00:40.000Z","msg":"想問下，如果有個freelance project，收左4成上期，做好左，等等下feedback 個客話唔做，但我其實己經做曬，咁尾數應該點？<br />\n<br />\n我係經中間人做的<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 照問，點會無<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 邊有得收"},{"pid":"6cb88e4ba5c5d89f0fa6e509164d3dd2135bbc6f","tid":409602,"uid":57633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:10:54.000Z","msg":"咁有無交過貨<br />\n<br />\n無交又無約<br />\n帳面上好難收喎<br />\n<br />\n利: 非freelance"},{"pid":"dcac8fd89d6044bbcc872634bf127041d5d2e76c","tid":409602,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:14:03.000Z","msg":"冇啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21b121b00f05113097ef430d118ed02af598e36b","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:18:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁有無交過貨<br />\n<br />\n無交又無約<br />\n帳面上好難收喎<br />\n<br />\n利: 非freelance</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢WORDPRESS 黎，淨係俾左 admin backend 我改，所以己經係佢度"},{"pid":"b296cb9ec98d1481b76c73c24b76933662c75e5f","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:19:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唉。。早知上期收50。。"},{"pid":"863ea51e64f4d0a9f4f69c7ca4eee35e60f01b61","tid":409602,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:20:15.000Z","msg":"freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31a42ddd791ec747aa0d30e8aa465ff66b855262","tid":409602,"uid":5015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:20:31.000Z","msg":"交左貨就要俾錢架啦"},{"pid":"5826b5a396d9115fc8253e40ebe8c60c2d009fa0","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:22:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個流程應該點？<br />\n<br />\n收上期-&gt;開工-&gt; 做好俾佢feedback-&gt;改feedback-&gt;收尾數<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁？"},{"pid":"87e62e11a25564477205d980cfcfde141c320d3c","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>交左貨就要俾錢架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都想問佢拎，但果個係中間人，我都唔知個客有無俾錢，所以想上黎問下。。。"},{"pid":"405d5ee1bc30d7de85979726531ec7d7fb320971","tid":409602,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:24:39.000Z","msg":"上去shut down 返個website 先la"},{"pid":"3c38555e5ebbcfa6a90a96ce4133adf6f02d1698","tid":409602,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:25:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個流程應該點？<br />\n<br />\n收上期-&gt;開工-&gt; 做好 <span style=\"color: red;\">(100% ?) </span>俾佢feedback-&gt;改feedback-&gt;收尾數<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁？</blockquote><br />\n做好晒 ? 全部比晒佢睇到 feedback ?"},{"pid":"5278f374fb1670455118513667d1f74a4db6c24d","tid":409602,"uid":17268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:25:22.000Z","msg":"or 如果個 website 有d 問題，出唔到住，佢應該就會搵你了"},{"pid":"eab8fba282b881c1cb9dcb6cdbe481b7cc4e5634","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:26:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個流程應該點？<br />\n<br />\n收上期-&gt;開工-&gt; 做好 <span style=\"color: red;\">(100% ?) </span>俾佢feedback-&gt;改feedback-&gt;收尾數<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁？</blockquote><br />\n做好晒 ? 全部比晒佢睇到 feedback ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做好曬佢一開始收上期果時既要求<br />\n<br />\n定應該呢個時候己經收左尾數先？<br />\n<br />\n但好似好多人都會借D 二唔俾住"},{"pid":"dd3469ac0522db9e34011d257345f94f19c0a5d8","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:27:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>or 如果個 website 有d 問題，出唔到住，佢應該就會搵你了</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪即係如果shutdown 左，佢都無搵我，即係個客堅唔做，唔洗諗尾數了？"},{"pid":"26f0427a3a4638c348389602a3ee02cb6656596b","tid":409602,"uid":57633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:28:29.000Z","msg":"幫佢還原返先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd347c2788ae69fca2a77c1c651658a04304ace6","tid":409602,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個流程應該點？<br />\n<br />\n收上期-&gt;開工-&gt; 做好 <span style=\"color: red;\">(100% ?) </span>俾佢feedback-&gt;改feedback-&gt;收尾數<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁？</blockquote><br />\n做好晒 ? 全部比晒佢睇到 feedback ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做好曬佢一開始收上期果時既要求<br />\n<br />\n定應該呢個時候己經收左尾數先？<br />\n<br />\n但好似好多人都會借D 二唔俾住</blockquote><br />\n咁你都知好多人借啲易唔比錢, 你都要諗下點保障自己架~<br />\n就算做好晒都唔好比晒佢睇, 又或者全部睇得但唔 work"},{"pid":"0cec77ecdc119a187e0ff25c12cce24a0ccc65c1","tid":409602,"uid":136645,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:30:17.000Z","msg":"香港IT的悲哀"},{"pid":"98c878f0062eaac04e0f7521e8bf76d8cabca196","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:33:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>freelance 就係咁架喇<br />\n<br />\n以後唔好做咁快喇~ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁個流程應該點？<br />\n<br />\n收上期-&gt;開工-&gt; 做好 <span style=\"color: red;\">(100% ?) </span>俾佢feedback-&gt;改feedback-&gt;收尾數<br />\n<br />\n唔係咁？</blockquote><br />\n做好晒 ? 全部比晒佢睇到 feedback ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n做好曬佢一開始收上期果時既要求<br />\n<br />\n定應該呢個時候己經收左尾數先？<br />\n<br />\n但好似好多人都會借D 二唔俾住</blockquote><br />\n咁你都知好多人借啲易唔比錢, 你都要諗下點保障自己架~<br />\n就算做好晒都唔好比晒佢睇, 又或者全部睇得但唔 work</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我有架。。。特登自己開左個SERVER，盡量問source code db dump 自己起。。<br />\n但今次係wordpress 唔俾access，得admin panel"},{"pid":"4997c9eebbce631d8f6998f53d3f928c8ac78f45","tid":409602,"uid":82425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:36:47.000Z","msg":"你做左比交左貨佢用唔用係一回事<br />\n錢就應該要照收<br />\n係餐廳叫左野食但上左菜先話都係唔食<br />\n唔通餐廳就唔收佢錢？<br />\n不過d 19客最鐘意走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申無做過freelance但聽講過有d客都拖勁耐先比尾數/走數"},{"pid":"46b94661c28dd4962073f19aa1564ddcd55c62ac","tid":409602,"uid":53194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做左比交左貨佢用唔用係一回事<br />\n錢就應該要照收<br />\n係餐廳叫左野食但上左菜先話都係唔食<br />\n唔通餐廳就唔收佢錢？<br />\n不過d 19客最鐘意走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申無做過freelance但聽講過有d客都<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">拖勁耐先比尾數/走數</span></strong></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n經常，唔問一定唔會俾"},{"pid":"641513ad8c3139949c0873f33e0e7c42c6a4a332","tid":409602,"uid":18740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T08:42:35.000Z","msg":"報警，你首先照如期交貨，再收尾數，唔俾就追佢"},{"pid":"94d78c7d3b7a65d0e5cf3fa6641c0a61a7c9c5c3","tid":409602,"uid":127469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:05:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你做左比交左貨佢用唔用係一回事<br />\n錢就應該要照收<br />\n係餐廳叫左野食但上左菜先話都係唔食<br />\n唔通餐廳就唔收佢錢？<br />\n不過d 19客最鐘意走數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申無做過freelance但聽講過有d客都拖勁耐先比尾數/走數</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢個尷尬位係未正式交貨。你個例子不無道理，但換過第二個角度睇又可以好唔同。<br />\n例如去買衫，用左間服裝公司提供嘅服務（要求職員俾件中碼你試、試身室），試左一輪，最後唔買，間服裝公司都唔會向你收錢。因為明碼實價嘅係件貨，而唔係個服務。如果份合約冇寫明收費係以服務為單位嘅話，中間就有好大嘅爭議空間。"},{"pid":"dfd9b364150c45fc493a14d294a2225df6b54f1a","tid":409602,"uid":2772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>交左貨就要俾錢架啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實我都想問佢拎，但果個係中間人，我都唔知個客有無俾錢，所以想上黎問下。。。</blockquote><br />\n中間人有做中間人既風險<br />\n<br />\n唔係個中間人一句<br />\n人地冇俾尾數<br />\n佢就可以唔找你數<br />\n<br />\n你當你同中間人之間有合約<br />\n而中間人同客之間又一份約<br />\n<br />\n你同中間人既約係你交貨果陣就已經完成左<br />\n佢唔找數你應該告佢<br />\n<br />\n個客唔找數亦應該由中間人告<br />\n唔洗勞煩你<br />\n<br />\n等D人成日覺得中間人好好搵<br />\n自己又做埋一份<br />\n唔出事尤自可<br />\n一出事兩邊都要煩"},{"pid":"9afd36c8b25ea787e43a0a096627135c4ba59027","tid":409602,"uid":64889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:15:43.000Z","msg":"緊係追啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8254c9255305c6b2fcb567744c8afead98212aa3","tid":409602,"uid":72647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-22T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"中間人還錢啦"}]}